睇左戒大便</blockquote><br />\n+1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n+1 仲想睇下有咩方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n+1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6f41d52f506e4661da41b6dc763d6bb5b37db42","tid":349674,"uid":113546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T17:01:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搵得唔係多<br />\n物價又好鬼貴<br />\n無特別做過乜<br />\n但個個月都儲唔到錢<br />\n有咩方法戒下大使</blockquote><br />\n認真答 搵個信得過既基金佬 幫你開返個儲蓄計劃<br />\n有啲每個月儲幾百蚊都夠<br />\n<br />\n最緊要逼到你儲錢 同埋有小小回報"},{"pid":"09371d042b88fcc9bce9cf3a4bf69b4d6ddb5eee","tid":349674,"uid":21664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T17:02:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇左戒大便</blockquote><br />\n+1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n+1 仲想睇下有咩方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n+1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n+1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"377043eda93036a30e1748ca2c359d326f26f20f","tid":349674,"uid":18271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T17:02:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>搵得唔係多<br />\n物價又好鬼貴<br />\n無特別做過乜<br />\n但個個月都儲唔到錢<br />\n有咩方法戒下大使</blockquote><br />\n認真答 搵個信得過既基金佬 幫你開返個儲蓄計劃<br />\n有啲每個月儲幾百蚊都夠<br />\n<br />\n最緊要逼到你儲錢 同埋有小小回報</blockquote><br />\n有買儲蓄保險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad9020c027deb48e19eb8295101b881348ab930a","tid":349674,"uid":65532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T17:06:22.000Z","msg":"不如講下大概每月儲到月入嘅幾成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fa9a7b753a1caeae883ddfe4c45f8ece4d1fc4d","tid":349674,"uid":18271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T17:20:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不如講下大概每月儲到月入嘅幾成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我諗一成都唔知有無<br />\n舊年又買左部MacBook pro<br />\n供緊24個月<br />\n仲有一半<br />\n有些少後悔<br />\n<br />\n其餘都係食野多<br />\n仲有供保險、上個月走去電髮<br />\n有個中同結婚我因爲做手術無去，請返佢食餐好<br />\n有d做完手術既保險未claim返<br />\n<br />\n其實主要都係出街食野多"},{"pid":"98783bb15e96a551ff66e2e1ee2d8b71f2e1607a","tid":349674,"uid":83527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T17:24:08.000Z","msg":"開1個流動戶口(出糧及基本洗費用)<br />\n1個儲蓄戶口(只儲及緊急時用)<br />\n一出糧就過數去儲蓄戶口<br />\n強制自己唔做任何分期去買野"},{"pid":"21779f11e1a5762d58c21cefa7bef8b5a3a52b39","tid":349674,"uid":18271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T17:28:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>開1個流動戶口(出糧及基本洗費用)<br />\n1個儲蓄戶口(只儲及緊急時用)<br />\n一出糧就過數去儲蓄戶口<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">強制自己唔做任何分期去買野</span></blockquote><br />\n呢次之後怕左<br />\n打死都唔再分期買野，除左電話"},{"pid":"3e94aaff9e20d790d4619c1f1d0fbad4497f78d6","tid":349674,"uid":100760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T17:29:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇左戒大便</blockquote><br />\n+1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n+1 仲想睇下有咩方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n+1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n+1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n+1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed8d30ed0afd700ce0808ca64a99b9a959a71278","tid":349674,"uid":100760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T17:30:35.000Z","msg":"不如樓主講下每個月大使左落邊度"},{"pid":"9d80f199612dcb1da751c094f8bd3098103b42a9","tid":349674,"uid":123524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T20:55:50.000Z","msg":"入 big4做 audit<br />\n包你有＄無時間冼"},{"pid":"65a4088fabd0402ec613976b9303be86ecca3043","tid":349674,"uid":30696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T01:37:51.000Z","msg":"睇咗大使（屎）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f6ab5f10552ce3595161e5cb8b38a2de54a73ab","tid":349674,"uid":53172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T01:40:27.000Z","msg":"少d 去大使館law<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d9f5c791b29d7ac101895c0e5161011bcb19771","tid":349674,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T02:04:20.000Z","msg":"食少啲嘢，平時食西餐囉、淨係食個食包"},{"pid":"d6e56e0ee526e6c6873cea59d830e204c7d297b0","tid":349674,"uid":66951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T04:23:16.000Z","msg":"唔食飯就唔會大使/有大便"}]}